================================================================================
DUNGEONS & DRAGONS 5TH EDITION SYSTEM REFERENCE DOCUMENT v5.1
================================================================================

The markdown files in this directory are derived from the Dungeons &
Dragons 5th Edition System Reference Document v5.1 ("SRD 5.1"), which is
made available by Wizards of the Coast LLC under the Open Game License
v1.0a and the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License
(CC BY 4.0).

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
UPSTREAM SOURCES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The original Markdown conversion of the SRD 5.1 was created by:
  - oldmanumby/dnd.srd.5.1  https://github.com/oldmanumby/dnd.srd.5.1

This project uses the remastered fork:
  - palikhov/DND5E.SRD.Wiki  https://github.com/palikhov/DND5E.SRD.Wiki

The conversion process consists of reformatting the SRD text into Markdown.
No game rules, spell descriptions, monster statistics, or other content have
been added beyond what is contained in the original SRD 5.1.

