--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CC BY 4.0 — ATTRIBUTION NOTICE (per the January 2023 release)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This work includes material taken from the System Reference Document 5.1
(https://dnd.wizards.com/resources/systems-reference-document) and is used
under the terms of the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 License (CC BY 4.0).

Modifications from the original SRD text: the text has been reformatted into
Markdown by the upstream contributors (oldmanumby, palikhov) and is
loaded by the Python engine in `src/auto_dm/phb/` for game-mechanics
purposes only. No substantive changes to game rules have been made.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PRODUCT IDENTITY
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Product Identity (as defined in section 1(e) of the OGL) is not used in
this project. Specifically: this project does not use the names "Dungeons
& Dragons", "D&D", or any Wizards of the Coast trademarks. Game content
(SRD 5.1) is loaded as data; no content is included that would prevent
this project from being distributed under the OGL/CC BY 4.0 terms.
